","msg":"<blockquote>好多南亞人幾融入我地<span style=\"color: red;\">中國</span>香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:19:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">5P殘體狗 Sky_Croc 又嚟搞事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Sky_Croc 事件撮要</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/14780/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/14780/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/06/001942_a79460cd1138de92ec127b087ddeaca6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F06%2F001942_a79460cd1138de92ec127b087ddeaca6.png&h=ea1111f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Sky_Croc真係高登最黑人憎嘅會員</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://hkgalden.com/view/103703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkgalden.com%2Fview%2F103703&d=u5qNS%2BofXBNJlJje3acABC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=f38a02ca\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkgalden.com/view/103703</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>雖則唔會再上高登留言但見到呢件人間垃圾都認唔住想鬧佢呢個殘體人<br />\n<br />\n呢條友成日扮哂野咁係各個ＰＯＳＴ到留言 <br />\n每次留親都用標準既殘體字 <br />\n呢條仆街係咪收左錢要潛移默化香港人用殘體？ <br />\n<br />\n我知道唔人已經ＢＬＯＣＫ左佢 <br />\n但係我仲見到呢條仆街ＫＥＥＰ住留言我真係眼火爆<br />\n<br />\n例子：＃８ <br />\n<a href=\"https://web.hkgolden.com/view/4694636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.hkgolden.com%2Fview%2F4694636&d=u5qNS%2BofXBNJlJje3acABC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=93bebebf\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.hkgolden.com/view/4694636</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>你老味Sky_Croc冇撚野下話, 個標題係繁體, 但個內文</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://web.hkgolden.com/view/5024501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb.hkgolden.com%2Fview%2F5024501&d=u5qNS%2BofXBNJlJje3acABC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=bf54590f\" target=\"_blank\">https://web.hkgolden.com/view/5024501</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>屌你老味</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">個標題係繁體, 但個內文都要打簡體?</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[CH13] 原來16年前&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum9.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5024283&amp;highlight_id=228121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum9.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5024283%26highlight_id%3D228121&d=u5qNS%2BofXBNJlJje3acABC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e9298693\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum9.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5024283&amp;highlight_id=228121</a><br />\n<br />\n[魚蛋論] 點解以前唔向中國移動執法???<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum9.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5021328&amp;highlight_id=228121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum9.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5021328%26highlight_id%3D228121&d=u5qNS%2BofXBNJlJje3acABC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e62b8851\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum9.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5021328&amp;highlight_id=228121</a><br />\n<br />\n[龍門系列] 相對於 香港人 同 新香港人<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum9.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5013720&amp;page=1&amp;highlight_id=228121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum9.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5013720%26page%3D1%26highlight_id%3D228121&d=u5qNS%2BofXBNJlJje3acABC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0ba441ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum9.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5013720&amp;page=1&amp;highlight_id=228121</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會員編號: 228121<br />\n膠名: Sky Croc<br />\n加入日期: 8/10/2009<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum9.hkgolden.com/ProfilePage.aspx?userid=228121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum9.hkgolden.com%2FProfilePage.aspx%3Fuserid%3D228121&d=u5qNS%2BofXBNJlJje3acABC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a48a9fd1\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum9.hkgolden.com/ProfilePage.aspx?userid=228121</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>佢幾年前就開始特登打簡體<br />\n<br />\n睇佢D語氣同用字同香港人一樣<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢係特登咁做，引人屌柒佢<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢係用心良苦，時時刻刻等人屌柒簡體<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係既話我屌佢全家</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1cd017f61858b497ff40b040be242b1350d9bb6f","tid":661190,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c3070fdec1f7188a90c52080bf754a12a43ab45","tid":661190,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44f7ac569e4d2602aa0d82f92bd7039246e8bb52","tid":661190,"uid":145496,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:09:05.000Z","msg":"我覺得連登係有一班五毛，不斷散播仇視南亞人既言論<br />\n你地睇下百份報就知<br />\n當然，仲有一大班on9仔一齊附和"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:50:38.000Z","msg":"獨醒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，身邊啲女性朋友無試過比南亞佬視姦同聊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:20:08.000Z","msg":"無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078cae9eba0a129245f82efb6f1db6f0a79a52ac","tid":661190,"uid":31423,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:24:38.000Z","msg":"有咩好吹奏，因為身邊嘅人係講廣東話啫<br />\n過幾年d 學生，超市收銀員，餐廳侍應個個都講蝗語，d 蝻咪學蝗語囉<br />\n講到佢地好愛本土咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0330b6549bfb71a7693e2063cbce6ec659865359","tid":661190,"uid":164799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T08:03:06.000Z","msg":"唔好on9 咩南亞人有好人有壞人  <br />\n20年前咪就係有班咁人講大陸人都有好有壞<br />\n你哋自己睇下今時今日乜撚野環境 <br />\non9 一次就算 唔好一直咁on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"